{"tid":2420992,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"中共打手 陳志豪 如何起家成軍 如何操盤極盡嗱喳 林鴻達 評論台 20210221","createTime":"2021-02-24T08:14:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-24T12:28:39.000Z","uid":78519,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"12fd7371dfb07e67c23c9689a846f965b2a8e0b6","tid":2420992,"uid":78519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T08:14:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nHNeQ3q7tfY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DnHNeQ3q7tfY&d=bCWCDjK20YNEqM2YtVdpm6crr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=4bf2c606\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nHNeQ3q7tfY</a><br />\n美國發表報告中共响社交網絡發放假消息操控輿論，其中一個被點名嘅人 #新民黨​ #陳志豪​。佢同 #容樂其​ #巫堃泰​ 等人早在十多年前的 #OurTV​ 已經係一夥。佢哋所進行嘅輿論操作，手法極度嗱喳，而我正正係身受其害<br />\n___________________<br />\n0:00​ 中共打手 陳志豪 如何起家成軍 如何操盤極盡嗱喳<br />\n3:30​ 陳志豪 容樂其 巫堃泰 嘅「結盟」，一切由十多年前的網絡多媒體平台 OurTV 開始<br />\n13:55​ OurTV 及直屬嘅組織 社區發展動力培育 (CDI) 由表面裝扮支持民主 到 鬼影處處<br />\n24:40​ 2018年3月台北一場研討會，CDI 的 #區贊年​ 極有可疑向中共報館通風報訊<br />\n28:01​ 陳志豪 整個集團操作輿論手法可謂相當精密，由有如CCTVB 造星吸納想上位願意受指揮嘅人<br />\n38:15​ Set Agenda 就是引導輿論、分散注意力、矇敝港人視野，俾共產黨做嘢<br />\n42:40​ 建立自家人事網絡，並聯外結盟，就是控制輿論<br />\n48:20​ 對未能吸納嘅人進行邊緣化、污名化，例如常對外「宣揚」我只係 悉尼老鼠<br />\n58:40​ Facebook YouTube 一直壓抑我發佈的內容的傳遞，就係配合陳志豪的操作<br />\n1:00:58​ Facebook 數據說明一切，朱西白格不容抵賴<br />\n1:09:01​ YouTube 賤招 - 唔識我尊姓大名唔會睇到我啲片<br />\n<br />\n___________________<br />\n<br />\n訂閱 Jacky Lim Channel  <a href=\"https://bit.ly/3n3H7vY​\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3n3H7vY%E2%80%8B&d=bCWCDjK20YNEqM2YtVdpm6crr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=5e1233df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3n3H7vY​</a><br />\n有請「課金」支持，多少不拘：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/3trvFgQ​\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3trvFgQ%E2%80%8B&d=bCWCDjK20YNEqM2YtVdpm6crr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=0d9949a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/3trvFgQ​</a><br />\n#StayHome​ #WithMe​ #跟我一起​ #宅在家​<br />\n<a href=\"https://jackylim.net/​\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjackylim.net%2F%E2%80%8B&d=bCWCDjK20YNEqM2YtVdpm6crr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=0835ee0d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://jackylim.net/​</a><br />\n___________________<br />\n更多汽車、巴士、小巴、運輸影片節目：<br />\nHK Bus Channel -<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/HKBusChannel%E5%B7%B4%E5%A3%AB%E5%8F%B0/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fc%2FHKBusChannel%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E5%258F%25B0%2F&d=bCWCDjK20YNEqM2YtVdpm6crr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=81cdbc2c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/c/HKBusChannel%E5%B7%B4%E5%A3%AB%E5%8F%B0/</a><br />\nHK Car Channel - <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/HKCarChannel%E6%B1%BD%E8%BB%8A%E5%8F%B0/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fc%2FHKCarChannel%25E6%25B1%25BD%25E8%25BB%258A%25E5%258F%25B0%2F&d=bCWCDjK20YNEqM2YtVdpm6crr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=77384c8a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/c/HKCarChannel%E6%B1%BD%E8%BB%8A%E5%8F%B0/</a>"},{"pid":"4a1bda306fb1632ad1b0651b9c6ee2ee5dda3ad6","tid":2420992,"uid":78519,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T09:33:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bb09ac05e5298a42e5fc83f1e7acbfe4e3e2709","tid":2420992,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T09:34:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e2973255c4a7427499cae55ccba2220794e7941","tid":2420992,"uid":78519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T09:35:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb0165656527d5d264c7adf7d737af7afaf387c7","tid":2420992,"uid":78519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0